            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>pineapple</strong></p><p>Tip: Keep the pineapple juice for your smoothies, cakes or marinades!</p><p>Dice the <strong>pineapple </strong>finely</p><p>Add the <strong>diced pineapple</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> to the bowl with the quick-pickled onion and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled</strong> <strong>pineapple salsa</strong></p>",
