      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>torn mushrooms</strong> and <strong>pepper strips </strong>with the <strong>red onion petals </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-7 min or until slightly charred</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? You may need 2 pans!</p>",
